<li class="rss-item"><a class="rss-item" href="http://www.ameinfo.com/bahraini-bank-shares-manama-market-afloat-352145"  title="The Bahrain All-Share Index closed 0.26% higher at 1,202.99 ..." target="_blank">Bahraini bank shares keep Manama market afloat</a> <br />
The Bahrain All-Share Index closed 0.26% higher at 1,202.99 points on Thursday amid muted trading. Only three shares gained, while no listed security lost value. Islami Bank Al Salam Bahrain (up), Bank of Bahrain and Kuwait and Ahli United Bank gained 2%, 0.98% and 0.72%, respectively.
</li>
<li class="rss-item"><a class="rss-item" href="http://www.ameinfo.com/crystal-helps-kuwait-city-celebrate-50-352144"  title="Crystal the world leading water feature specialist, with off..." target="_blank">Crystal helps Kuwait City celebrate 50 years of its Constitution with water feature</a> <br />
